        "text": "=*🚨 ERROR en N8N Workflow 🚨*\n\n*Workflow:* {{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"workflow_name\"] }}\n*Error:* {{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"error_message\"] }}\n*Node:* {{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"last_node\"] }}\n*Exec ID:* {{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"execution_id\"] }}\n\n[Ver Detalles]({{ $node[\"Global Config\"].json.N8N_EDITOR_BASE_URL }}/workflow/{{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"workflow_id\"] }}/executions/{{ $node[\"Format Error Payload\"].json[\"execution_id\"] }})",
        "additionalFields": {
